title: KUNMI Women's Skinny Ripped Trendy Jeans Distressed Stretchy Denim Pants
description: A version of the skinny fit, these mid waisted distressed jeans offers a comfortable wear with a power stretch denim fabrication featuring the highest elastic and recovery.
This slim fit jeans for women finished with classic wash and raw tassel hem. Cute destroyed details at the leg. Five-pocket construction.
Engineered with an eased belt loop waistband that prevents both gapping and muffin top.

These women distressed jeans are suitable for Casual Outtings, School, Vacation, Picnic, Traveling, Driving, Home, and Daily Wear. These will be an excellent gift for your friends at any festival, for example, Christmas Day, Birthday, Valentine's Day.
